    "description": "Cyberlinks Co., Ltd. provides various cloud services primarily in Japan. It operates through four segments: Distribution Cloud, Government Cloud, Trust, and Mobile Network. The company offers Cloud EDI platform, cloud-based headquarters core system, ID-POS analysis service, shelf allocation management system, and EDI business support services for retailers. It also offers local government digital services, comprehensive disaster prevention system service, information services, and local government website creation, operation and maintenance services; and CloudCerts, a blockchain-based digital certificate issuing service; and range of trust services utilizing My Number Card. In addition, the company provides system service for educational institutions, and product information and image database; and operates DoCoMo shops that sell mobile phones and computers. Further, it provides cable television and rental server services, medical information system, hardware maintenance, and sales management systems for specialty stores. Cyberlinks Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1964 and is based in Wakayama, Japan."
